  "instructions": [
    "Combine mung bean sprouts, Australian bush tomato chutney, coconut oil, ginger, garlic, and lime juice in a large bowl.",
    "Grill the mixture over medium-high heat for 3-4 minutes per side, or until the sprouts are tender and char-grilled.",
    "Transfer the cooked mixture to a serving platter and sprinkle with sesame seeds, salt, and black pepper.",
    "If desired, drizzle with peanut butter for added creaminess.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro and serve immediately with a lazy Susan spinner."
